### Test 1: Get all pending approval requests
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/approvals/pending
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test 2: Create new instrument (will trigger approval request with Action=Create)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/instruments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "TEST001",
  "name": "Test Instrument 001",
  "description": "Testing approval flow"
}

### Test 3: Update instrument (will trigger approval request with Action=Update)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/instruments/{{instrumentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "symbol": "TEST001_RENAMED",
  "name": "Test Instrument 001 Renamed",
  "description": "Updated description"
}

### Test 4: Block instrument (will trigger approval request with Action=Block)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/instruments/{{instrumentId}}/block
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test 5: Unblock instrument (will trigger approval request with Action=Unblock)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/instruments/{{instrumentId}}/unblock
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test 6: Delete instrument (will trigger approval request with Action=Delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/instruments/{{instrumentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test 7: SuperAdmin approves own Create request
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/approvals/{{createRequestId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test 8: SuperAdmin approves own Update request  
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/approvals/{{updateRequestId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

