### Test 12: Reject a pending request
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/approvals/{{requestIdToReject}}/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Test rejection - needs review"
}

### Test 13: Add comment to request
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/approvals/{{requestId}}/comment
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "comment": "This request needs further investigation"
}

### Test 14: Check all requests after approvals
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/approvals
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
